snippet.title: Ari Global Show
snippet.description:
‘ Ari Global Show’ focuses on motivational and global  entertainment interviews. 

The  principal goal and the main purpose of each interview is to inspire people through the  interviewer’s stories. 

Our host ‘Ari Global’ is a well known Bilingual (Spanish/ English) TV host. She has interviewed top celebrities such as Jennifer Lopez, Ozuna, Amy Schumer, Vanessa Hudgens, Shaquille’ Oneal, Luis Fonsi, Eva Longoria, Samuel Jackson, Gerald Butler, among others. 

She began creating her own content and some of her interviews have surpassed  big TV latin networks views.  One example would an  interview  where she reached 3.5 millions views.

She believes that everyone has a story to tell and to be inspired by it.
So enjoy and possibly get inspired by listening to our podcasts.


@Ariglobalshow
Tv host @ariglobal 



Email : ariglobalshow@gmail.com
